                Lupus anemola <note>sic</note> <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ic</abbr></expan> <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ave</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="2"/>tat <note>sic</note> quot <note>sic</note> comidi <note>sic</note> mecum <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ave</abbr></expan><supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <note>sic</note> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ego Maurentia <lb n="2"/>in hunc <note>sic</note> mo<lb break="no" n="3"/>numentum <note>sic</note> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">tit</supplied>ulu<supplied reason="lost">m p</supplied>osui Lupo <lb n="5"/>virginio meo cum <supplied reason="lost">q</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/>uem <note>sic</note> quinquaginta a<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"/>nis beni <note>sic</note> laboravi adqu<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <lb n="8"/>inculpatim co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>vixi</abbr></expan> et A<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied><lb break="no" n="9"/>genteo Samarconi fr<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied><lb break="no" n="10"/>tris <note>sic</note> vel subulel<expan><ex>la</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> m<supplied reason="lost">atri</supplied><lb break="no" n="11"/>s meae ipsum titul<supplied reason="lost">um</supplied> <expan><abbr>feci</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberfläche stark verrieben; etliche Buchstaben, die bei der Auffindung noch lesbar waren, sind nicht mehr zu erkennen (besonders in Z. 1, 2 und 7). Metrik: Z. 1-2. Z. 1 u. 2 befinden sich auf der corona. Z. 11: Samarconi könnte auch Dativ von Samarco sein.</p>
            </div>
